:0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T08:35:27.000Z","msg":"我都有幫襯過，店主好撚黃<br />\n痴撚線，佢執左隻咩野怪獸返來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xGZaF73.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxGZaF73.png&h=a44bf3b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60822414861277d85351a1cb548be02cd098cf5b","tid":2020620,"uid":23405,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T08:43:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OL6o1ab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOL6o1ab.png&h=7ee6fdac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rseBBJx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrseBBJx.png&h=b48fb473&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EYsrYWT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEYsrYWT.png&h=14e2dcf4&s={SIZE}\" /> 616已經開始表態啦，仲收留手足。"},{"pid":"5dc073b2d1b60af65f40ae236c125ed45341db5a","tid":2020620,"uid":23405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T10:49:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfdbd1ab282888bb07dbb04f74027ae314bbab31","tid":2020620,"uid":23405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T10:49:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe937b33dae44b274cd927974cc37fbbd210251","tid":2020620,"uid":23405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T10:49:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/